title: ACR122U Software Development Kit SDK
description:
=======================================
ACR122U SDK CD
=======================================

Contents: 

Demo Programs
- NFC Peer-to-Peer Demo
- Visitor Management System Demo

Tools & Utilities
- ACR122U Tool
  Lets you to perform reader and card-related commands
- QuickView
  Checks for proper driver installation
- ACS Easy Key
  Allows you to change Mifare security settings
- ACR122U Scripting Tool
  Allows you to send a sequence of commands to contactless cards
- Sample codes
  Demonstrates basic commands used to communicate with the cards and readers
Available in the following programming languages: Java, Delphi 7, Visual Basic 6, Visual C++ 6, Visual C++ 2005 (x64), Visual C# 2005 and Visual Basic .Net 2005
Smart Card Reader Driver(s)

Reference Manual(s)
